# ================================
# DEPLOYMENT NOTES
# ================================
#
# REQUIRED VARIABLES (must be set):
# - NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL
# - NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY
# - SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY
# - OTP_SECRET
#
# HIGHLY RECOMMENDED:
# - RESEND_API_KEY (for contact form and password reset emails)
# - UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_URL + TOKEN (for rate limiting)
# - NEXT_PUBLIC_GTM_ID (for analytics)
#
# OPTIONAL:
# - All business info and social media variables
#
# SECURITY CHECKLIST:
# ✓ Enable Row Level Security (RLS) on all Supabase tables
# ✓ Configure storage bucket policies in Supabase
# ✓ Set up email templates in Supabase (if using Supabase Auth emails)
# ✓ Enable realtime on required tables (projects, hero_sections, showreels, activity_logs)
# ✓ Never commit .env.local to version control
# ✓ Use different secrets for development and production
# ✓ Rotate secrets regularly
#
# DATABASE SETUP:
# - Run SQL scripts from Non-essentials/database-setup-scripts/
# - Or import complete schema from complete-schema.sql
# - Verify RLS policies are active on all tables
#
# VERCEL DEPLOYMENT:
# 1. Connect repository to Vercel
# 2. Set all required environment variables in Vercel dashboard
# 3. Deploy from main branch
# 4. Test admin login and password reset flow
# 5. Verify contact form sends emails
# 6. Check analytics tracking works